text: Extremely friendly and courteous staff. I have NEVER seen a Pizza Hut like this. Itâ€™s clean. Food came out immediately. Employees had manners. Crazy!! Solid job Carter Enterprises, Pizza Hut owes you for reversing their usual franchise location trends. Thanks!

name: Brian McWilliams
text: Stopped here on the back end of a loooong drive. Hadn't had dine-in at a Pizza Hut since I was a kid and was pleasantly surprised. Pizza Hut delivery is fine, but a fresh pie was much better. Tables and floor were dirty and not being actively cared for. Seemed fairly new and well lit. Bathrooms were a little dingy too.

name: Melissa Trice
text: This is our favorite place to get pizza on the way home from our parents.  We order on the app and it's always ready on time. Our pizzas are always hot and fresh.  So far, we have not had a pizza made incorrectly so that's a plus as well.

text: Food was great. Everyone's food arrived but mine. By the time I got my Athenian Salad, everyone is almost finished eating.
